/i
[Bowling: Instructions

Playing as Burns, you must score three
strikes in order to win. Furthermore, Ohms
must not hit a single pin.

To bowl, push the arrow button in the
control area in the lower left. This will
fire a bullet upwards from the button. If
the bullet hits the aiming bar, Burns
scores a strike. Otherwise, Burns loses.

SAVE NOW.]
/i
